<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/stressTask.css" />

        <title>Stress Task</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
        <section>
            <div>
                <h1>Stress Task</h1>
                <h2>Instructions</h2>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>As soon as you click start, a timer of
                        <b>120 seconds</b> will appear.
                    </li>
                    <li>You have to perform mental arithmetic and select the correct
                        option from the given 4 options.
                    </li>
                    <li>Get <b>75 questions right in 120 seconds</b> and then the
                        task is complete.
                    </li>
                    <li><b>Every wrong answer will deduct 10 seconds</b> from the
                        timer thus making it difficult to complete the task.
                    </li>
                    <li>If you can get 75 questions right in 120 seconds, the task
                        is completed successfully and you should feel relatively
                        more stressed.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <b>Feel free to do the task multiple times to induce more stress.</b>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <div class="quiz-box">
            <div class="start-div">
                <button id="start" class="button-67" role="button">Start Task</button>
            </div>
            <div class="game-content">
                <div class="timer-div">
                <h2 id="timer"></h2>
            </div>
            <div class="score-div">
                <h3 id="score"></h3>
            </div>
            <div class="question-div">
                <h2 id="question"></h2>
            </div>
            <div class="answers-div">
                <button id="option1" class="button-67"></button>
                <button id="option2" class="button-67"></button>
                <button id="option3" class="button-67"></button>
                <button id="option4" class="button-67"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="answer-text-div">
                <h3 id="answer-text"></h3>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
        


    </body>
    <script src="js/tokenAssigner.js"></script>
    <script src="js/stressTask.js"></script>

    <%- include('partials/logout-script') %>
</html>
